<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.1.4">
<l>pāvi yātucey tāyeṉ ṉeñcamē paṇṭu toṇṭucey tārai maṇmicai</l>
<l>mēvi yāṭkoṇṭu pōyvi cumpēṟavaik kumentai</l>
<l>kōvi nāyakaṉ koṇṭa luntuyar vēṅka ṭamalai yāṇṭu vāṉavar</l>
<l>rāvi yāyirup pāṟka ṭimaittoḻil pūṇṭāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My heart, you acted without deliberating: you assumed the duty of service</l>
<l>To the one who has become the soul of the celestials,</l>
<l rend="indent">ruling on high Vēṅkaṭa Mountain where clouds rise,</l>
<l>The lord of the gopi-s, our father who, dwelling on earth long ago,</l>
<l>Having taken as devotees those who did service [to him],</l>
<l rend="indent">lifted [them] to heaven.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
